{"data":[{"date":"07:41 24/06","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn t\u1eed chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/rudy-chan-thuong-lo-tran-gap-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sebastian Rudy \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi b\u1ecb g\u00e3y m\u0169i \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>Rudy ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u0129nh tr\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t ch\u1ec9 sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 ngay sau khi Rudy r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ola Toivonen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u201cC\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u00fd ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Marco Reus g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat. Trong 45 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rudy ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rudy ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/rudy-chan-thuong-lo-tran-gap-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Rudy ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 95, Toni Kroos m\u1edbi t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Joachim \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rudy v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cSebastian Rudy c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb g\u00e3y m\u0169i. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ch\u1ea3y m\u00e1u n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n sau. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd v\u00e0 xem m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ra sao\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ee9c thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Rudy, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Jerome Boateng v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n khi th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span> c\u00f2n 8 ph\u00fat. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Reus b\u1ecb chu\u1ed9t r\u00fat trong 10 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i c\u00f2i. Boateng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n, Rudy th\u00ec g\u00e3y m\u0169i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i h\u1ecd 2 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i xem m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMats Hummels c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u0103ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-loew-lai-gay-bao-khi-tai-hien-man-an-ri-mui-421-189386.html\">HLV Joachim Loew l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n \u0103n ... r\u1ec9 m\u0169i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"519","checkdouble":"189387"},{"date":"08:00 24/06","title":"Kroos gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c, Hummels v\u1eabn lo \u00e2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hummels-tang-boc-kroos-sau-man-giai-cuu-dt-duc-ngoan-muc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Mats Hummels tin r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Toni Kroos</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng khi \u0111\u1ec3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\" target=\"_blank\">ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a Kroos</span> \u1edf ph\u00fat 95 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u201cC\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eafm trong tay quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft cho chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Hummels \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng mang t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hummels lo l\u1eafng cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi th\u1eafng th\u00f3t tim Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hummels lo l\u1eafng cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi th\u1eafng th\u00f3t tim Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Hummels-lo-lang-cho-DT-Duc-sau-khi-thang-thot-tim-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hummels lo l\u1eafng cho \u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kroos l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00fd g\u00ec. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Hummels lo l\u1eafng cho tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 World Cup \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi t\u00f3m t\u1eaft cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Fisht Stadium \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Hummels cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua Mexico ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 xem li\u1ec7u m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. B\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i cho ch\u00fang ta ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rudy-chan-thuong-lo-tran-gap-han-quoc-469-189387.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn t\u1eed chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-dau-tim-cua-dt-duc-421-189380.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111au tim c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"518","checkdouble":"189392"},{"date":"08:16 24/06","title":"Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Osorio v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/nhe-nhang-ha-han-quoc-osorio-van-chi-trich-trong-tai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.</h2><h2>HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a TP.HCM tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 23/6, CLB TP.HCM b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p 2, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Minh Trung ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TPHCM h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TPHCM h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/1529763879_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Miura t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ta ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed an to\u00e0n. \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, CLB TP.HCM bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1ed1ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo t\u00f4i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d, HLV Miura n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Minh Trung c\u1ee7a TP.HCM l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh chia s\u1ebb: \u201cV\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p hai th\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i sai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c TP.HCM, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018 \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng khi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f9ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\">Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"517","checkdouble":"189393"},{"date":"07:56 24/06","title":"Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Miura b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i t\u0103ng cao.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: start; \"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ea1i V-League</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 23/6, hai CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, TP.HCM x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 13 v\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, HLV Miura c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, HLV Miura c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/1529763926_7.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miura c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 TP.HCM c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i binh Matias Gonzalez. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t V-League hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho CLB TPHCM t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5, \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb bi\u00ean tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Phi S\u01a1n, Gonzalez ch\u1ea1y c\u1eaft m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap TP.HCM thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n \u2018h\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u2019 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Khi hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u00f4i qua \u00edt ph\u00fat, CLB TP.HCM li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi H\u1eefu \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 L\u00ea S\u1ef9 Minh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef t\u1edbi h\u1ebft 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn TP.HCM cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u1ea5y lu\u00f4n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB TP.HCM c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"516","checkdouble":"189394"},{"date":"08:02 24/06","title":"Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</h2><h2>SLNA k\u00e9o d\u00e0i m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 3</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB SLNA \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/danh-bai-binh-duong-hlv-slna-het-loi-khen-vien-binh-tu-flc-thanh-hoa.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League, SLNA ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0<span style=\"background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: Arial;\">Ng\u00f4 Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 44 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</span>. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV SLNA \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng cho hay: \u201c\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i, t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 3 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.\u00a0Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean tr\u00ean h\u1ebft. D\u00f9 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u1eeda tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u1ea3 quan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League-2018.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"515","checkdouble":"189395"},{"date":"08:06 24/06","title":"HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi TP.HCM xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.</h2><h2>HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a TP.HCM tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 23/6, CLB TP.HCM b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p 2, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Minh Trung ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TPHCM h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TPHCM h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/1529763879_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Miura t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ta ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed an to\u00e0n. \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, CLB TP.HCM bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1ed1ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo t\u00f4i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d, HLV Miura n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Minh Trung c\u1ee7a TP.HCM l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh chia s\u1ebb: \u201cV\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p hai th\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i sai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c TP.HCM, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018 \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng khi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f9ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\">Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"514","checkdouble":"189396"},{"date":"08:13 24/06","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 15 V-League: N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/sau-vong-15-vleague-nong-cuoc-dua-tru-hang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP.HCM. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng n\u0103m nay th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.</h2><h2>1. N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 TP.HCM trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 23/6, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbp hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 TP.HCM v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay c\u00e0ng th\u00eam n\u00f3ng khi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean th\u00ec SLNA v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chu\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 15 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 15 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i TP.HCM c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng V-League th\u00eam k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 TP.HCM. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, vi\u1ec7c C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. Ch\u1ec9 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111i\u1ec3m, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng san b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac hi\u1ec7p 1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 74 v\u00e0 90\u2019+3 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 5-2 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs Da Nang\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/ha-noi-vs-da-nang-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i '\u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p' ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 15 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gia t\u0103ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm n\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. HAGL c\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL vs Sai Gon\" title=\"HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/05_saigon_hagl_140418_anhkhahoa06_tydi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 ghi li\u1ec1n 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ngo\u1ea1i binh Da Sylva c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 trong l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. V-League \u2018thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec7t\u2019 v\u00ec World Cup<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i V-League k\u00e9m s\u1ee9c h\u00fat m\u00f9a World Cup l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u khi m\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ea1i tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian World Cup di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn ra \u1edf v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. CLB HAGL v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat nh\u1ea5t V-League c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 thu h\u00fat 5 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 6 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"San Hang Day\" title=\"S\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/san_hang_day.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby v\u1eafng v\u1ebb t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 4 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn kho\u1ea3ng\u00a01/4 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ed9i c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u00e8o t\u00e8o m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. Sau s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda \u0111\u00f4ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a V-League khi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea1t x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 ho\u1eb7c h\u01a1n 10.000 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 HAGL, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh,\u2026 th\u00ec s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 lu\u00f4n \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao kho\u1ea3ng 14 \u0111\u1ebfn 15.000 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3n \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 V-League k\u00e9m s\u1ee9c h\u00fat khi m\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 VCK World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh-168-189396.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh-168-189396.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi TP.HCM xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\">Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"513","checkdouble":"189397"},{"date":"08:35 24/06","title":"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/cau-thu-mexico-van-khiem-ton-du-da-buoc-mot-chan-qua-vong-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng Mexico v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e1nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Mexico c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/cau-thu-mexico-van-khiem-ton-du-da-buoc-mot-chan-qua-vong-bang.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u00e2y ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Mexico kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Osorio \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00f4m qua.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u1ea3ng F tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, n\u1ebfu Mexico thua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f2n \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Mexico ch\u1ee7 quan l\u00e0 ch\u1ebft</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 El Tri mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho Mexico m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb g\u00ec n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ecbch s\u1eed\u201d, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Guardado chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i lu\u00f4n d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miguel Layun c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Mexico l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn Mexico vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhe-nhang-ha-han-quoc-osorio-van-chi-trich-trong-tai-469-189393.html\">Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Osorio v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-han-quoc-vs-mexico-461-189376.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-2 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"512","checkdouble":"189398"},{"date":"08:22 24/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal (22h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6): Kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-senegal-22h00-ngay-246-khoc-liet-tam-ve-di-tiep.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u1eb1m s\u1edbm c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 5 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t. N\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n h\u1ecd. T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 penalty c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00f9 tang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1edbi 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho h\u1ecd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Senegal thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ebfu tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal (22h00 ng\u00e0y 246) Kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal (22h00 ng\u00e0y 246) Kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Nhat-Ban-vs-Senegal-(22h00-ngay-246)-Khoc-liet-tam-ve-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><i>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Samurai xanh?</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 4 k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean khi 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi. N\u0103m 2002, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. T\u1edbi n\u0103m 2010, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt l\u1ea1i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Cameroon \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. \u0110i\u1ec3m chung c\u1ee7a hai k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y l\u00e0 khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia ch\u00e2u Phi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2014 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Ph\u00ed \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u1ede nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Hy L\u1ea1p, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, l\u00fac n\u00e0y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi Senegal \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi m\u00e0 Senegal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Senegal \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c Senegal ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Senegal v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Colombia v\u00e0 Ba Lan k\u1ebft th\u00fac b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng H \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 \u00edt ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh dung tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi VCK World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh b\u1edfi &ldquo;Samurai xanh&rdquo; b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby ho\u00e0i nghi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay t\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u1ec9 2 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd G.&nbsp;Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ph\u1ea3i h\u1ea1 Senegal, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Senegal kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, \u0110T Senegal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ba Lan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng trong t\u1ed1p 10 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 16 b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i - Robert Lewandowski.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, Senegal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi Senegal \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac cau thu Senegal an mung chien thang khi tieng coi man cuoc vang len.\" title=\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c vang l\u00ean.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Mbaye-Niang-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Ba-Lan-vs-Senegal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u01b0 Balde Keita, Kouyate, M'Baye Niang v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, Sadio Mane \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hai \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111o\u00e1n ra c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u00e0nh cho Senegal v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1edd th\u1eddi c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018, Senegal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ciss\u00e9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Aliou Ciss\u00e9 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1edfi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Senegal trong 90 ph\u00fat s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Senegal ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau 3 l\u1ea7n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Senegal th\u1eafng hai, h\u00f2a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ba l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t giao h\u1eefu.&nbsp;Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua 5 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, bao g\u1ed3m 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ukraine, Ghana v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, gi\u1edd Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Paraguay (giao h\u1eefu) r\u1ed3i Colombia (World Cup 2018).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKeisuke Honda \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6/8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf World Cup, v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Senegal m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1/11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 h\u00f2a Uzbekistan 1-1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ba Lan, d\u00f9 b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 ph\u1eadn chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Senegal thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 sai l\u1ea7m d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&nbsp;Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal:</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nhat Ban vs Senegal\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Nhat-Ban-vs-Senegal-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n&nbsp;Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal: 2-1</strong><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"511","checkdouble":"189399"},{"date":"08:50 24/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama (19h00 ng\u00e0y 24/06): V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Tam s\u01b0?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-panama-19h00-ngay-2406-ve-di-tiep-cho-tam-su.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Tam s\u01b0, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang x\u1ebfp b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng G s\u1ebd gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng G, Anh \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Tunisia. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1t khao v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama (19h00 ng\u00e0y 2406) V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Tam s\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama (19h00 ng\u00e0y 2406) V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Tam s\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Anh-vs-Panama-(19h00-ngay-2406)-Ve-di-tiep-cho-Tam-su-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 2-1 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 70% song Anh g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh Tunisia. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft, Tam s\u01b0 c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu tinh t\u1ebf \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, Anh c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 61%, tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 18 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 8 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Dele Alli, Raheem Sterling hay Jesse Lingard \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i sao anh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gareth Southgate l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 15 b\u00e0n sau 25 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao c\u1ee7a Kane, HLV Southgate co\u0301 m\u00f4\u0323t c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 co\u0301 th\u00ea\u0309 ta\u0323o ra kha\u0301c bi\u00ea\u0323t va\u0300 la\u0300m b\u00e2\u0301t c\u01b0\u0301 ha\u0300ng pho\u0300ng ng\u01b0\u0323 na\u0300o cu\u0303ng pha\u0309i lo l\u0103\u0301ng. Ngo\u00e0i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs, Kieran Trippier, Jordan Henderson, Ashley Young c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHenderson l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Trippier v\u00e0 Young l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n song Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup 2018. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Panama, \u0111\u1ed9i thua 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Anh vs Panama\" title=\"Preview Anh vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2462018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Anh vs Panama l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Southgate s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia. Sterling ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Harry Kane cho Rashford. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-tru-cot-421-189015.html\" target=\"_blank\">Dele Alli ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> v\u00e0 Loftus-Cheek c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Tam s\u01b0, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang x\u1ebfp b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng G s\u1ebd gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tusia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n B\u1ec9 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu anh c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng B\u1ec9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Anh s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p <br>\r\nv\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang n\u1eb1m ch\u1eafc trong tay Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Panama kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n Tam s\u01b0</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Panama gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 3-0 Panama\" title=\"B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Bi-3-0-Panama-Khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Panama g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a B\u1ec9 0-0 sau hi\u1ec7p 1, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7p 2 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c 0-3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Panama kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 (MLS).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, tr\u1eadn Anh vs Panama th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hernan Dario Gomez bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam s\u01b0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0ng Panama ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPanama \u1edf th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh, song ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Trung M\u1ef9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam s\u01b0.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Anh vs Panama\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Anh vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Anh-vs-Panama-(3-5-2-vs-4-1-4-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Anh vs Panama</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"510","checkdouble":"189401"},{"date":"22:31 23/06","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 s\u1ed1ng d\u1eady t\u1eeb c\u00f5i ch\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ket-qua-duc-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2><h2>Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien-463-189371.html\" target=\"_blank\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u1ee8C VS TH\u1ee4Y \u0110I\u1ec2N</span><br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"509","checkdouble":"189371"},{"date":"23:19 23/06","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3ng G g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\u2026 bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n bi\u1ec3u d\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273294/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n1. B\u1ec9 t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Tunisia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoberto Martinez c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 c\u00e1ch Tunisia t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea7ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf ra sao trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, v\u1eady n\u00ean HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u0169 b\u00e3o h\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1edbm</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Kevin De Bruyne \u00e1n ng\u1eef tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ed9 tam v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 n\u00ean nh\u1edb b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng, trong khi m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5 Axel Witsel c\u00f9ng wing-back hai c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2ng cao d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng co c\u1ee5m v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</span>.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTam t\u1ea5u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Romelu Lukaku, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Dries Mertens \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Tunisia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecb qu\u1ea7n th\u1ea3o v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1, v\u1edbi then ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Hazard gi\u00fap mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n t\u1eeb trong tr\u1ee9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc. 84 ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, B\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">2. B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi &ldquo;hot trend&rdquo; c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKi\u1ebfm t\u00ecm \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o \u0111i m\u00f2 kim \u0111\u00e1y b\u1ec3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhan hi\u1ebfm khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n m\u00e0 Tunisia hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin khai th\u00e1c, v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a d\u00e1m nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B, C&hellip; \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ho\u1eb7c xoay chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i khi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 5-2 Tunisia\" title=\"B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/231459-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: B\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ec3 b\u00e0n thua &ldquo;kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n&rdquo; ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 an b\u00e0i, tuy\u1ec3n Anh n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Tunisia ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n: \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t &ndash; t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh &ndash; \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. So v\u1edbi c\u1ea5p CLB th\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf World Cup, tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ee9u c\u00e1nh cho s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi. B\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t cho Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00f2ng knock-out trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3. Hazard x\u1ee9ng danh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ed5 ra xoay quanh t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng trao cho Hazard tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 khi b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard Bi vs Tunisia\" title=\"Hazard B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: Hazard ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Vincent Kompany v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 anh. Ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u1ef1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Lukaku trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u, k\u00e9o theo 45 ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man Utd v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Panama.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Tunisia, vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Hazard c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t De Bruyne kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thua k\u00e9m c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng ni\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf con khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc b\u1eb1ng qu\u1ea3 penalty &ldquo;t\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfm t\u1ef1 \u0103n&rdquo;, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n cho c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Lukaku.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Hazard c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi pha x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. 21 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t kho\u00e1c \u00e1o B\u1ec9, Hazard in d\u1ea5u gi\u1ea7y trong 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi 11 v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 12.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4. C\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh ti\u1ec5n Tunisia v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, hai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u00edt \u1ecfi m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Tunisia ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ch\u00e2u Phi x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t FIFA.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh Tam S\u01b0, ngay c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e1t m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i h\u1ed9t v\u1edbi Tunisia trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. V\u1eady n\u00ean d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: C\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t ch\u1ec9 sau 5 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, khi c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng c\u1ea9u th\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Syam Ben Youssef mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hazard th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Tunisia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u01a1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n oan u\u1ed5ng b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean v\u1ea1ch 16m50.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c2u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u1ec9 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0 Tunisia \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd c\u00f3 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 xi\u00ean th\u00eam 4 nh\u00e1t dao k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee5c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 cho nhau \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c xa v\u00e0 Panama c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. Sau chi\u1ec1u mai theo gi\u1edd Nga, b\u1ea3ng G s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c an b\u00e0i hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 m\u00e1y bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Bi 5-2 Tunisia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Thong-ke-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-tunisia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-tunisia-vs-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia (KT): Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1o m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Spartak</span><br>\r\nHai ng\u00f4i sao thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Hazard vs Lukaku thay nhau l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"508","checkdouble":"189373"},{"date":"00:06 24/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u00fat bay \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ra kh\u1ecfi World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/nguoi-thuy-dien-tuyen-bo-sut-bay-dkvd-duc-ra-khoi-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2><em><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh video (B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV)</span></strong></em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c: Reus (48'), Kroos (90'+5)<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: Toivonen (32')<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c: Manuel Neuer; Joshua Kimmich, Antonio Rudiger, Jerome Boateng,  Jonas Hector; Sebastian Rudy, Toni Kroos; Marco Reus, Thomas Muller,  Julian Draxler; Timo Werner. <br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: Robin Olsen; Mikael Lustig, Victor Lindelof, Andreas  Granqvist, Ludwig Augustinsson; Viktor Claesson, Sebastian Larsson,  Albin Ekdal, Emil Forsberg; Ola Toivonen, Marcus Berg. <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"507","checkdouble":"189374"},{"date":"00:29 24/06","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ed9n b\u1ec1 \u00e2u lo, v\u1ee5 Leroy Sane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u01a1i l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/tuyen-duc-bon-be-au-lo-vu-leroy-sane-duoc-khoi-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Lothar Matthaus v\u00e0 Michael Ballack \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ng\u1ea7m ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao Man City c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u01a1i l\u1ea1i</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ee5 Leroy Sane b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ee5 Leroy Sane b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/tuyen-duc-bon-be-au-lo-vu-leroy-sane-duoc-khoi-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leroy Sane b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u01a1n c\u1ea3 v\u1ee5 Radja Nainggolan v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, vi\u1ec7c Leroy Sane kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, bao g\u1ed3m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng lao \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb hay nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00e2u lo b\u1ed9n b\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf Mannschaft, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng: \u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn Mexico v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn Leroy Sane v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c, Michael Ballack c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cJoachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 t\u1ea5n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Leroy Sane, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho ch\u00fang ta.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cChuy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 l\u00fd khi Leroy Sane m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Man City. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sao? T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u1eeb phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u1eafm r\u00f5 v\u00e0 anh ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh Loew th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien-463-189371.html\"><im